content.rendered:
Directed by Prawaal Raman.

Written by Mike Flanagan. Jeff Howard. Prawaal Raman. Prawaal Raman. Prawaal Raman. Prawaal Raman.

Cast Adil Hussain(Alex Merchant). Huma Qureshi(Natasha). Madalina Bellariu Ion(Ana). Lisa Ray(Liza Merchant). Saqib Saleem(Kabeer). Parimal Aloke(Michael). Richard Banks(Police Officer 383). Paul Blackwell(Police officer). Lee Nicholas Harris(Arresting Police Officer492). Chris Martin Hill(Arresting Police Officer191). Jassie Mortimer(Arresting WPC 109). Rob Oldfield(Jack). Darcie Rose(Model (as Darcie Lincoln)). Rysa Saujani(Young Natasha). Abhishek Singh(Young Kabeer)

Languages Hindi. English.

Producers James Edgar. Marc D. Evans. Mike Flanagan. Jeff Howard. Vikram Khakhar. Anil Kurian. Trevor Macy. Aniruddha Nag. Cyrus Patel. Prawaal Raman. Dharmendra Rawal. Ishan Saksena. Sunil Shah. Manav Shrotriya. Jigar Suchak. Suraj Wadhwa. Tullika Sonam Wangdi.

Production B4U Television Network. Intrepid Pictures. Relativity Media.
